<li>Aldo Mieli, <i>La science arabe</i>, Leiden, 1938, pp.&#160;8, 16.</li>
<li>Nasr, <i>Science and Civilization in Islam</i>, see. Razes: <i>The Secret of Secrets</i>, p.&#160;273, also pp.&#160;197–200, and Anawati: <i>L'Alchemie arabe in Rased.</i></li>
<li><span class="citation book"><a href="Edward_Granville_Browne" title="Edward Granville Browne">Browne, Edward Granville</a> (2001). <i>Islamic Medicine</i>. Goodword Books Pvt. Ltd.. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/81-87570-19-9" title="Special:BookSources/81-87570-19-9">81-87570-19-9</a>.</span></li>
<li><a href="../../w/index-title=M._M._Sharif&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="M. M. Sharif (page does not exist)">M. M. Sharif</a>, <i>A History of Muslim Philosophy</i></li>
<li>Walker, P. "The Political Implications of al-Razi's Philosophy", in C. Butterworth (ed.) <i>The Political Aspects of Islamic Philosophy</i>, Cambridge, MA: <a href="Harvard_University_Press" title="Harvard University Press">Harvard University Press</a>, 61-94.(1992)</li>
<li>Motazed, K. <i>Mohammad Zakaria Razi</i></li>
</ul>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Muhammad_ibn_Zakariya_al-Razi&action=edit&section=32.php.html" title="Edit section: Encyclopedia">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Encyclopedia">Encyclopedia</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><cite id="refRichter-Bernburg"><span class="citation book">Richter-Bernburg, Lutz. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/hawi-medical-book">"AL-ḤĀWI"</a>. <i>Encyclopaedia Iranica</i>. <b>1</b>. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/0-933273-54-1" title="Special:BookSources/0-933273-54-1">0-933273-54-1</a><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/hawi-medical-book">http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/hawi-medical-book</a></span>.</span></cite></li>
